						               													<description>Explore the magical Filipino folklore of Lagim! Lagim is a one-of-a-kind fantasy card game inspired by Fillipino myths and folktales. Lagim offers a unique and action packed gaming experience made more immersive by its authentic roots and its gorgeous and evocative art. With so many exciting ways to play you deicde your fate-an enthralling game at every turn. Lagim invites you to a fantastic realm of monsters, mayhem, and magic - play the game and discover the thrilling stories and exciting encounters we've carefully woven for you.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;No matter who you are and where you are from, an amazing adventure full of infinite possibilities awaits! In this game about strategy and luck. Lagim can be played by 3-6 players. Each player takes turns battling monsters and each while defending their bargyos. During each players turn they are reffered to as the active player. The active player is allowed to play 1 game action each turn and they cannot pass; this action depends on their current cards and strategy and their turn ends once an action has been performed or a battle has been concluded.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;The game board is split into 2 realms the forest realm sits at the center of the play area. Each player starts with 3 souls. The last player alive with remaining souls is declared the winner.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;mdash;Description From The Publisher&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
